Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 我的鼻子沒有聞錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈到底裝在哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在這種情況下 還能裝出一副無辜的樣子 真是好膽量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 是否要讓我來問問你的身體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:39.94,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:42.19,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思念越發強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:46.32,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}無法傳達到這份祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:52.91,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}一定是因為	迷失了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:01:00.63,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}無論何時  只有被映在這眼瞳裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:04.09,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}是唯一的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:07.26,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}一直如此堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:11.43,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}世界並非唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:15.18,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}還有所謂如果的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:19.19,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}因為存在著無限可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:24.82,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}正迷失著方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:28.57,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}想要見你 卻覓不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.57,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}不論你現在身處何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:33.78,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}必定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:39.46,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}不慎闖入了瞳中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:41.13,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:45.38,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被黑暗之手遮蔽了去路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:49.51,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被怯弱的心所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.30,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}也不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:55.89,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}繼續尋找著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:39.94,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:42.19,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思いつのるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:46.32,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}この祈りが届かないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:52.91,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}何かをきっと 見失ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:01:00.63,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いつだって この瞳に 映されたものだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:04.09,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}唯一の真実だと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:07.26,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}信じていたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:11.43,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}世界は一つじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:15.18,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}もしもという世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:19.19,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}無限にあるとして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:24.82,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いま途方に暮れている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:28.57,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.57,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いま何処にいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:33.78,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}必ず見つけ出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:39.46,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷い込んだのは瞳の中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:41.13,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:45.38,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}例え暗闇がゆく手を遮り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:49.51,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}弱気な心惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.30,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}諦めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:55.89,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}探しつづけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\fad(800,1000)\be1\bord2\4a&Hc1&\3a&Hc1&\shad3\pos(523,365)}蓉 子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不快點坦白 可是會讓這個身體受傷的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼非得待在這麼寒冷的地方呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那種黑暗而又狹窄的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏可是既寬闊風景又好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑 什麼也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊賞著雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很風雅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看周圍 冰天雪地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且一片漆黑什麼也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事能稱得上什麼風雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燙熱的酒一下子就結成冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在在在幹什麼呀 這可不是開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣去會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手呀 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼 惡魔 神不會饒恕你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小健結成冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣啊 兄弟 要不要一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你一副慌張的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒有 沒有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 這個那個的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是慌慌張張\N急急忙忙的 到底是為了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人太少 完全賣不出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 反正最初就沒什麼期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 你知道初美在哪裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嗎 在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 有一套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是去找房間裏的男子 就再也沒看見他的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可疑了 快去找出那個男子來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找房間裏的男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是前面那閒客房的旅客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的同伴突然感到腹痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我正在到處詢問有誰帶了藥來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那真是不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 是那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 只能一個個挨著搜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題好像不是你同伴的腹痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有帶就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在出去的話 可是又會遭遇同樣的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是肌肉 那個胸脯的鼓起也太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰看到都會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我到也聽過有那種興趣的女性\N在男裝時會想辦法將胸脯隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天老是踫到同行的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個人想讓你見一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟我走一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓我見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連禮服都借用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是生意上的東西 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你非常適合這身打扮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西伯利亞之虎 這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要來直接與我接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我告訴她這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是根據實際情況的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在知道相互的身份才能處於有利的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被手冊或是命令束縛住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這一行中可是很難生存下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 一起喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裏面沒人嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來陪陪我吧 喂 裏面有人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 您這樣我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請回你的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別煩我 別以為我是二等乘客就小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 請回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在進行一個重要的商談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否請不要打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是商談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 你這樣讓我很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎樣的商談啊 能否也讓我參加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否把暗號解讀本交給我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否請您安靜一點呢 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可不是一般的乘務員與醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 果然先裝上保險是正確的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保險?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這輛列車被裝上了炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一定能時間內 我不去復位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和列車一起 解讀本也會消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我死了那麼就一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 別小看人 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來可是這位姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解讀本 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 在哪裏 到底放在哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想在這個亞爾卡迪亞 做出藍色的天空的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺到不在這個空中庭園 做出一個向日葵的小山是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 說到對於向日葵的小山來說 必要的東西 還是教會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來 你們還想參加我的造城活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那真是奇妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得有人確實說過下次在我面前出現時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對、一定會將那個 智慧之光的根源夏娃一起帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不是 哪裏弄錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒有說過\N「絕對」、「一定」之類的話的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛的 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能得到夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國家就會比現在更加的美好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如是這樣的話 為什麼夏娃不在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格爾剛裘亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過生氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會讓皮膚開裂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你擔心非常的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後就讓塞倫來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你們所知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是一個純粹的妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是屬於惡魔的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她將出手幫助我們尋找夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 接著就讓我們\N回到夜行列車的故事裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底變成什麼樣子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒被打中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在問出之前就把他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 多少也知道了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個乘務員與這個男人是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是西伯利來之虎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是 也有需要扮演那個角色的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 時代已經變化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這種三流的男人竟然被派到第一線來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就當當你的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是很適合那身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對這項工作來說 最需要到不是體力或年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是經驗啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗號本一定就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把剛才從那年輕男人那裏得到的東西交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不反抗就不會受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底藏在哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從那男人那裏拿到了什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這東西給你的男人\N在這輛列車是裝了定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有什麼線索
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人從一等車廂的洗手間出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人從這裏出來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在拍掉什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經找到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是空的 裏面什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼會沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是葉月的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你到底去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 打開了打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到一個時鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運氣真好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是保護我自己而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是一個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職業罷了 一點也高興不起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉月 快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個世界已沒有什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個旅行到底會持續到何時呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點找到夏娃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊的身體先撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要光看著出神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著走啊 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:41.45,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠の祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:48.17,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.09,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}どんなに遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:02.47,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}きっと捕まえてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:10.23,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕との それが約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:17.28,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思いでも 抱きしめないでいても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:24.70,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}気持ちは 一つも届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:33.09,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠お祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:39.84,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:48.73,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕の間にひかる夜明けをみつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.86,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,500)}もらすぐ始まる明日を迎えにゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:41.45,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}獻上永遠的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:48.17,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}切莫放棄珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.09,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}無論多麼遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:02.47,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}也一定要抓住給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:10.23,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}那是你我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:17.28,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}即使抱著回憶哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:24.70,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}任何心情也無法傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:33.09,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}獻上永遠的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:39.84,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}切莫放棄珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:48.73,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}去發現在你我之間閃亮的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.86,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,500)}迎接即將開始的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這本夜行列車的書裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒找到初美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 還是偷看一下下一本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「暗與帽子與書之旅人」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請繼續欣賞下一回的故事
